nitroshare (0.3.4-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add support for device discovery via mDNS
  * Add quarantine mode for receiving transfers
  * Add Arabic, German, Italian, & Polish translations
  * Add button to open transfer directory to transfer window

 -- Nathan Osman <nathan@quickmediasolutions.com>  Mon, 16 Oct 2017 13:26:06 -0700

